<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7763649c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410yy–1"><num value="410yy–1">§ 410yy–1.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this subchapter, the term—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7763649d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410yy–1/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> “Commission” means the Keweenaw Historic Preservation Advisory Commission established by <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s410yy–8">section 410yy–8 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7763649e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410yy–1/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> “park” means the Keweenaw National Historical Park established by <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s410yy–2/a/1">section 410yy–2(a)(1) of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7763649f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410yy–1/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> “Secretary” means the Secretary of the Interior.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id776364a0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/543/s2">Pub. L. 102–543, § 2</ref>, <date date="1992-10-27">Oct. 27, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/3570">106 Stat. 3570</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
